  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK225">
<l>āṟṟuvā rāṟṟal paciyāṟṟa lappaciyai</l>
<l>māṟṟuvā rāṟṟaliṟ piṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The power of those who perform penance is the power of enduring hunger. It is inferior to the power of those who remove the hunger (of others).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
